            "text": {
              "status": "generated",
              "div": "<div xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml\"><h3>Annotation</h3><table class=\"hl7__eu__lab__report\"><tr><th>Conclusion and Recommendations based on this report and previous findings known to us</th></tr><tr><td>The patient shows elevated HbA1c, indicating suboptimal long-term glycemic control (prediabetes/diabetes range). Chloride is mildly elevated and total CO₂ is slightly low, which may suggest a mild metabolic acidosis or compensation. Other parameters are within normal limits. Clinical correlation and further evaluation of acid-base status and glycemic management are recommended.</td></tr></table></div>"
